query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, s.totalAmount, s.saleDate, s.projectId, p.name as projectName, p.includeInReports 
FROM services s 
LEFT JOIN projects p ON s.projectId = p.id 
WHERE s.saleDate >= '2025-07-01' AND s.saleDate <= '2025-07-31'
ORDER BY s.saleDate;
